@api_gateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5220
@api_gateway_HttpsAddress = https://localhost:7191

### Health Check (if available)
GET {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

### Register User
POST {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Login
POST {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Get Current User (requires JWT token)
# @name login
POST {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Extract token from login response and use it
GET {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Refresh Token
POST {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Logout (requires JWT token)
POST {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### Get Bot Detection Analyses (requires JWT token)
GET {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/botdetection/analyses
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Start Bot Analysis (requires JWT token)
POST {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/botdetection/analyze
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "socialAccountId": "guid-here",
  "socialNetwork": "VK"
}

### Get VK User Profile (requires JWT token)
GET {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/socialaccounts/vk/users/12345/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Get OK User Profile (requires JWT token)
GET {{api_gateway_HostAddress}}/api/socialaccounts/ok/users/12345/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json
